Amel Moussa bụ onye Tunisia na-ede uri, onye nkuzi na onye nta akụkọ
O bipụtara akwụkwọ uri abụọ, a sụgharịwokwa uri ya n'asụsụ Italian, Spanish, French, Polish, German na Czech
O ritere ihe nrite (National Creative Award) nke Tunisia maka uri ya na ihe nrite sitere na Arab Women Organization maka ọrụ mgbasa ozi ya na Tunisia.
